{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day/task-21","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 21","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Esteban kaže zbogom i nada se da će te videti sutra. Koristi prijateljski izraz kako bi to pokazao, zatim dodaje uobičajeni pozdrav za oproštaj kako bi završio razgovor.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj/Slušajte zvuk i dovrši/dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta mañana</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Chao</span> su prijateljski načini za oproštaj na španski.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta mañana</span> znači \"Vidimo se sutra\". Koristi se kada očekuješ da ćeš nekoga videti sledećeg dana.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Chao</span> To je uobičajena forma \"kwaheri\" koja se koristi u nekim špansko govornim zemljama. To je isto kao \"bye\". Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta mañana. Chao.</span> – Vidimo se sutra. Zdravo.</p>\n<p>Postoje dve uobičajene varijante pisanja za reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chao</span>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Chao</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> je najpoznatiji u Španiji, Čileu i Kolumbiji.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Chau</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> se često koriste u Argentini, Urugvaju i Paragvaju.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day/task-21"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK. BLANK.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Hasta mañana","feedback":"<p>Ovaj izraz ima <strong>dve reči</strong> i znači \"Vidimo se sutra\". Koristi se kada očekuješ da ćeš nekoga videti sledećeg dana. Prvo slovo prve reči je veliko, a zapamti da koristiš slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ñ</span> u drugoj reči.</p>"},{"answer":"Chao","feedback":"<p>Ovo je neformalni način za oproštaj. Ova razlika se završava sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, a ne <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>. Prvi slovo je veliko.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-boardmeeting.png","characters":[{"character":"Esteban","position":{"x":50,"y":25,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_greetings_in_the_evening.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":5.35,"finishTimestamp":7.11},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.87,"dialogue":{"text":"Hasta mañana.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.22,"finishTime":2.76,"dialogue":{"text":"Chao.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.26,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day","dashedName":"task-21","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-greetings-and-farewells","block":"es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-pract